    </section>
    <section id="services" class="service">
      <Heading
        Sub="Our Services"
        label="Intelligent Solutions for a Digital World."
      />
      <div class="service-container">
        <div class="service-tabs">
          <div class="service-item item-automation active" data-tab="1">
            <h5>Intelligent Automation & Data</h5>
          </div>
          <div class="service-item item-develop" data-tab="2">
            <h5>Modern Development & Delivery</h5>
          </div>
          <div class="service-item item-tech" data-tab="3">
            <h5>Infrastructure & Emerging Tech</h5>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="service-wrapper">
          <div class="service-content-list list-automation active" data-tab="1">
            <div class="service-content">
              <div class="service-list">
                <h5>Artificial Intelligence Development (AI & ML)</h5>
                <p class="para">
                  Building custom predictive models, natural language processing
                  (NLP) systems, and computer vision applications that automate
                  complex decisions and uncover deeper insights.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="service-list">
                <h5>Data Analytics & Business Intelligence</h5>
                <p class="para">
                  Transforming fragmented data into cohesive, visual dashboards
                  and reports. We provide the clarity needed for strategic
                  planning and real-time decision-making.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="service-list">
                <h5>Chatbot Development (AI & ML)</h5>
                <p class="para">
                  Deploying sophisticated, conversational AI agents powered by
                  machine learning for customer service, lead generation, and
                  internal support automation.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="service-list">
                <h5>RPA (Robotic Process Automation)</h5>
                <p class="para">
                  Implementing software robots to handle high-volume, repetitive
                  business processes, freeing your team for higher-value,
                  strategic work.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="service-content-list list-develop" data-tab="2">
            <div class="service-content">
              <div class="service-list">
                <h5>End-to-end Web Development with UX/UI Design</h5>
                <p class="para">
                  Full-stack application development from concept to launch. We
                  guarantee user-centric design (UX/UI), secure architecture,
                  and optimal performance across all platforms.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="service-list">
                <h5>Mobile App Development</h5>
                <p class="para">
                  Creating intuitive, high-performance native (iOS/Android) and
                  cross-platform mobile applications designed to maximize
                  engagement and utility.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="service-list">
                <h5>SaaS Products Development</h5>
                <p class="para">
                  Partnering with you to ideate, build, and scale your
                  proprietary Software-as-a-Service platform. We focus on
                  recurring revenue models and robust cloud architecture.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="service-content-list list-tech" data-tab="3">
            <div class="service-content">
              <div class="service-list">
                <h5>Cloud Deployment</h5>
                <p class="para">
                  Strategy, migration, and management of scalable cloud
                  environments (AWS, Azure, GCP). Ensure security, cost
                  efficiency, and DevOps best practices from day one.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="service-list">
                <h5>IoT Development</h5>
                <p class="para">
                  Connecting physical devices and sensors to the cloud. We
                  specialize in secure data ingestion, device management, and
                  building user interfaces for large-scale IoT networks.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section id="portfolio" class="portfolio dark-section">
      <Heading Sub="Selected Works." label="Real Solutions. Proven Scale." />
      <div class="portfolio-wrapper">
        {
          portfolioData.map((portfolio) => (
            <Portfolio
              title={portfolio.title}
              category={portfolio.category}
              desc={portfolio.desc}
              service={portfolio.service}
              link={portfolio.link}
            />
          ))
        }
      </div>
    </section>
    <section id="approach" class="idea">
      <Heading
        Sub="Great Methodology"
        label="Structured, Transparent, Guaranteed."
      />
      <div class="idea-wrapper">
        <div class="idea-content">
          <AboutCard
            heading="The Client-Centric Process"
            content="We follow a lean, iterative Agile methodology for maximum flexibility and transparency."
          />
          <AboutCard
            heading="Our Quality Guarantee"
            content="We Stand By Our Code. We prioritize clean, well-documented code and comprehensive testing. We offer a 30-day post-launch warranty on all custom development to ensure stability and immediate support."
          />
          <AboutCard
            heading="Technology Stack Confidence"
            content="Modern Tools for Future-Proof Solutions. We select technology based on performance, scalability, and security. We leverage Python, React/Vue, Node.js, and leading cloud infrastructure to build solutions that will last."
          />
        </div>
        <SectionHeader label="Approach" />
        <div class="idea-points">
          <Chip
            content="Discovery & Strategy: Define the problem and map the technical solution."
            heading="Step 1:"
          />
          <Chip
            content="Prototype & Design: Create clickable wireframes and high-fidelity UI/UX."
            heading="Step 2:"
          />
          <Chip
            content="Development Sprints: Build in short cycles, sharing progress every two weeks."
            heading="Step 3:"
          />
          <Chip
            content="Quality Assurance & Launch: Rigorous testing and secure, smooth deployment."
            heading="Step 4:"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section id="about" class="about dark-section">
      <Heading
        Sub="About Nalivance"
        label="Driven by Expertise. Defined by Results."
      />
      <div class="about-content">
        <div class="about-wrapper">
          <div class="about-list">
            <AboutCard
              heading="Our Origin Story"
              content="Founded by a team of technology veterans frustrated by the inefficiency of legacy IT firms. We started with a clear mission: to deliver cutting-edge AI and Data solutions with the speed and personal touch of a highly specialized startup."
            />
            <AboutCard
              heading="The Team"
              content="While we are a startup, our core leadership brings decades of combined experience from Fortune 500 companies in AI engineering, data science, and enterprise architecture. Your project is managed by experts, not interns."
            />
          </div>
          <div class="about-list">
            <div class="about-card">
              <h5>Our Core Values</h5>
              <p class="para">
                <span>Transparency:</span> Clear communication and honest feedback
                at every stage.
              </p>
              <p class="para">
                <span>Innovation:</span> Constantly researching and applying the latest
                advancements in AI and Cloud.
              </p>
              <p class="para">
                <span>Accountability:</span> We own the outcome and deliver on our
                promises.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
